Building Lyrabar

See doc/readme-qt.rst for instructions on building Lyrabar-Qt,
the intended-for-end-users, nice-graphical-interface, reference
implementation of Lyrabar.

See doc/build-*.txt for instructions on building lyrabard,
the intended-for-services, no-graphical-interface, reference
implementation of Lyrabar.

Further build information and documentation is available at
the official Lyrabar website, http://www.lyrabar.org
